Installation instructions
-------------------------

== Requirements ==
If you find that this script works with any older versions of these 
applications, please drop me a note at and@vmn.dk.

Tested with Perl version 5.8.8

fortune (for !fortune functionality)

= Perl modules =
File::Copy
Getopt::Long
POE v.0.9500
POE::Component::IRC v.5.16
Term::ReadKey v.2.30
HTML::Entities v.1.35
DBI v.1.52 and up
DBD::SQLite v.1.12
LWP::UserAgent v.5.805

== Installation ==
1) tar zxvf anna-$VERSION.tar.gz
2) cd anna-$VERSION/
1) sudo make install
2) refresh your path (or just run /usr/local/bin/anna)
3) type "anna"
4) ???
5) PROFIT!!!

See HELP or anna --help for more info on how to run Anna^
